      "instruction": "<p>Once the mince is browned, reduce the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add your <strong>dried thyme </strong>to the pan with your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> flour </strong>and stir with a wooden spoon for a further 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
